---
alwaysApply: true
rules:
  - name: Tailwind CSS
    description: Use Tailwind CSS for styling
    howToFollow:
      - Use the `@tailwind` directive to import Tailwind CSS
      - Use the `@apply` directive to apply Tailwind CSS classes
      - Use the `@layer` directive to group Tailwind CSS classes
      - Use the `@screen` directive to apply Tailwind CSS classes at different screen sizes
      - Use the `@variants` directive to apply Tailwind CSS classes at different variants
      - Use the `@responsive` directive to apply Tailwind CSS classes at different responsive breakpoints
